metadata.name: Trapped by Desire
metadata.description:
Trapped by desires. 

Desires and dreams that lurk in people's hearts and minds. Shackled by morality and social roles, desiring what society condemns, you drown in your own thoughts. Break the shackles and become free, or stay caged, abandoning your true self. 

Which will you choose? 

1/1 art, 4724*5906 pixels 300 DPI
